      <title>法国共和党乔蒂派将派出 62 名候选人参加选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-republicans-ciotti-wing-to-field-62-candidates-in-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国共和党埃里克·乔蒂一派已与极右翼国民联盟结盟，将在法国立法选举第一轮中仅派出 62 名候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-republicans-ciotti-wing-to-field-62-candidates-in-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:46:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
