      <title>哥伦比亚法官可能否决左翼领导人的养老金改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/colombian-judges-likely-to-kill-leftist-leader-s-pension-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据接受彭博社采访的宪法专家称，哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗 (Gustavo Petro) 提出的加强国家对养老金控制的旗舰计划很可能会被该国最高法院否决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/colombian-judges-likely-to-kill-leftist-leader-s-pension-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 19:23:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
